{"tid":1028083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊岳橋考察大灣區：行程務實，寄語港青年應放眼四周多區發展！","createTime":"2019-02-19T08:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T09:22:35.000Z","uid":49388,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a0f753754a4ee5b611cc9cc088d7bc4950509b6","tid":1028083,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1378303/org/1db1130a9113d5e4ecbe800ebb8f26b4.jpg/q-7o1PGNKlxcPDlnLl8qesTiISf0eEULZz2GKWc9hik?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1378303%2Forg%2F1db1130a9113d5e4ecbe800ebb8f26b4.jpg%2Fq-7o1PGNKlxcPDlnLl8qesTiISf0eEULZz2GKWc9hik%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=58dc1968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公民黨黨魁楊岳橋表示，本身對行程無特別期待，只是平常心和客隨主便，不過認為行程務實。他又認為年青人不應把自己的發展局限在任何一個地方，很多年青人也放眼四周，重點是香港政府有否努力留下人才。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席胡志偉則表示，行程看到內地的科技發展一日千里，而香港相對起來，推動創科主動性不足。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【大灣區】首日行程結束　楊岳橋指行程務實<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/180475/大灣區-首日行程結束-楊岳橋指行程務實\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F180475%2F%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80-%E9%A6%96%E6%97%A5%E8%A1%8C%E7%A8%8B%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F-%E6%A5%8A%E5%B2%B3%E6%A9%8B%E6%8C%87%E8%A1%8C%E7%A8%8B%E5%8B%99%E5%AF%A6&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=299b632b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/180475/大灣區-首日行程結束-楊岳橋指行程務實</a>"},{"pid":"b9c0be163abb21e58c88003cf3ba42327743f1cc","tid":1028083,"uid":35221,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.litenews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/24775093_2003868722987073_6126012559069880785_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.litenews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F24775093_2003868722987073_6126012559069880785_n.jpg&h=b4d80082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eWDjTP5.jpg\" data-thumbn